Rotten Tomatoes (raw)
This is a movies app displaying box office and top rental DVDs using the Rotten Tomatoes API.

Time spent: <11+ hours>

Features
Required

[2] User can view a list of movies. Poster images load asynchronously.
[1] User can view movie details by tapping on a cell.
[1 Using MBProgressHUD] User sees loading state while waiting for the API.
[1.5 ] User sees error message when there is a network error: http://cl.ly/image/1l1L3M460c3C
[0.8 ] User can pull to refresh the movie list.
Optional

[2] Add a tab bar for Box Office and DVD.
[ ] Implement segmented control to switch between list view and grid view.
[1.5 Not working] Add a search bar.
[ ] All images fade in.
[0.5] For the large poster, load the low-res image first, switch to high-res when complete.
[0.6 bring side effects using UIColor so I disable] Customize the highlight and selection effect of the cell.
[ ] Customize the navigation bar.
